room_title: Escape room "An Hour to Kill" by Exit Game in Los Angeles
room_address: 111 N. Atlantic Blvd., #148 Monterey Park, CA 91754
room_description: Come and be a part of James Bond's last adventure. James is on his last mission before retirement when he went missing. You, England's best agents must figure out a way to get through all the security systems in Military Intelligence (section 6) and the vaunted training facilities and danger room. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to find out what happened to Bond on his final mission.
